     10
  NOSPLIT

 ARRAYSIZES
    MAXATT 16
    MAXAA2 11
    MAXNRP 17
    MAXNBT 15
    MAXBNH 12
    MAXBON 14
    MAXTTY 14
    MXQHEH 12
    MAXTH  16
    MAXQTY 10
    MAXHIH 10
    MAXQHI 10
    MAXPTY 11
    MXPHIH 16
    MAXPHI 10
    MAXCAG 11
    MAXAEX 20014
    MXEX14 16
 END ARRAYSIZES
   
   FORCEMATCH
     rEAD REF TRAJ  FILE
      ref_TRAJECTORY 
     READ REF FORCES
     rEAD REF STRIDE
      40
     EQUIVALENCIES
      3
      2 4
      3 5
      6 7
     cHARGES FIX
      1
     1  0.801
     WQ INDIVIDUAL
      1
      1 100.0
     WQ GENERAL
      0.01
     WV
      0.1
